body_html: This has been fixed by bazelbuild/bazel@ed7ced0. Try using Bazel at HEAD. A new Bazel will be cut in a few days. As soon as that happens, the TensorFlow repository will be updated to use multiple mirrors for each external file.

body: This has been fixed by https://github.com/bazelbuild/bazel/commit/ed7ced0018dc5c5ebd6fc8afc7158037ac1df00d. Try using Bazel at HEAD. A new Bazel will be cut in a few days. As soon as that happens, the TensorFlow repository will be updated to use multiple mirrors for each external file.
